Cthulu: a MEAN stack Single Page template
MongoDb, AngularJs, ExpressJs, Node.js, PassportJs, Mongoose, Zurb Foundation, Gulp, SCSS, Angular ui-router, ejs, SweetAlerts

to launch a server on port 3000
>nodemon
or
>npm start
---------------------------
to install nodemon
> npm install -g nodemon
---------------------------

to compile SCSS into CSS, open a second tab in terminal and
>gulp

gulp will watch for changes in the SCSS file and compile as you build

---------------------------
to install gulp
> npm install -g gulp
---------------------------
